; pnpm config for the shared textsearch lib's dev-only gates (typescript + biome).
; minimum-release-age is in MINUTES; 14400 = 10 days. Supply-chain guard: never
; install a version published less than 10 days ago, so a compromised release has
; time to be caught before it enters a build. pnpm (not npm) is the reason.
minimum-release-age=14400
